quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,64,"A sì mú ìjọ kejì (ìyẹn, ìjọ Fir‘aon) súnmọ́ ibẹ̀ yẹn."
  26,65,"A gba (Ànábì) Mūsā àti gbogbo àwọn tó ń bẹ pẹ̀lú rẹ̀ là pátápátá."
  26,66,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A tẹ ìjọ kejì rì (sínú agbami)."
  27,37,"Padà sí ọ̀dọ̀ wọn. Dájúdájú à ń bọ̀ wá bá wọn pẹ̀lú àwọn ọmọ ogun tí wọn kò lè kojú rẹ̀. Dájúdájú a máa mú wọn jáde kúrò nínú (ìlú wọn) ní ẹni yẹpẹrẹ, tí wọn yó sì di ẹni àbùkù.”"
  27,38,"(Ànábì Sulaemọ̄n) sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ìjòyè, èwo nínú yín l’ó máa gbé ìtẹ́ (Bilƙīs) wá bá mi, ṣíwájú kí wọ́n tó wá bá mi (láti di) mùsùlùmí.”"
  27,39,"‘Ifrīt nínú àwọn àlùjànnú sọ pé: “Èmi yóò gbe wá fún ọ ṣíwájú kí o tó dìde kúrò ní ibùjókòó rẹ. Dájúdájú èmi ni alágbára, olùfọkàntán lórí rẹ̀.”"
  28,10,"Ọkàn ìyá (Ànábì) Mūsā pami (lórí ọ̀rọ̀ Mūsā, kò sì rí n̄ǹkan mìíràn rò mọ́ tayọ rẹ̀) ó kúkú fẹ́ẹ̀ ṣàfi hàn rẹ̀ (pé ọmọ òun ni nígbà tí wọ́n pè é dé ọ̀dọ̀ Fir‘aon) tí kò bá jẹ́ pé A kì í lọ́kàn nítorí kí ó lè wà nínú àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo."
  28,11,"Ó sì sọ fún arábìnrin rẹ̀ pé: “Tọ ipa rẹ̀ lọ.” Ó sì ń wò ó láti ibi tó jìnnà. Wọn kò sì fura (sí i)."
  28,12,"A kò sì jẹ́ kí ó mu ọyàn (mìíràn) ṣíwájú (tìyá rẹ̀.) (Arábìnrin rẹ̀ sì) wí pé: “Ṣé kí èmi júwe yín sí ará ilé kan tí ó máa gbà á tọ́ fún yín? Wọn yó sì jẹ́ olùtọ́jú rẹ̀.”"